<h5 class="exercise">
<span class="type">Exercise</span> <span class="acro">HSE.T10</span> <span class="contributor"><a knowl="./knowls/contributor.martinjackson.knowl">Martin Jackson</a></span>
</h5>
<div class="problem"><p>Prove or disprove:  A system of linear equations is homogeneous if and only if the system has the zero vector as a solution.
</p></div>
<div class="solution"><p><a knowl="./knowls/solution.HSE.T10.knowl">Solution</a></p></div>
</div><div class="exercise" acro="HSE.T11">
